License: AGPL-3.0-or-later (see LICENSE in this directory).

The files are copied into the IrohLocation Expo module because the Rust `blew`
backend requires Android Kotlin managers and JNI callbacks in the application
classloader. No functional modifications were made when vendored in July 2026.
